At 835 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking strong thunderstorms along a line extending from 6 miles south of Tilghman Island to Coles Point. Movement was east at 45 mph. HAZARD...Winds in excess of 40 mph. Rainfall 1 to 2 inches.
